<li><i><a href="/wiki/%C3%89p%C3%AEtre_%C3%A0_l%27Auteur_du_Livre_des_Trois_Imposteurs" title="Épître à l'Auteur du Livre des Trois Imposteurs">Épître à l'Auteur du Livre des Trois Imposteurs</a></i> (1770)</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Plays" id="Plays"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Voltaire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Plays">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Plays</span></h3>
<p>Voltaire wrote between fifty and sixty plays, including a few unfinished ones. Among them are these:</p>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Oedipe(play)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Oedipe(play) (page does not exist)">Œdipe</a></i> (1718)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Zaire_(play)" title="Zaire (play)" class="mw-redirect">Zaïre</a></i> (1732)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Eriphile&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Eriphile (page does not exist)">Eriphile</a></i> (1732)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Ir%C3%A8ne&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Irène (page does not exist)">Irène</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Voltaire%27s_Socrates_(play)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Voltaire's Socrates (play) (page does not exist)">Socrates</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Mahomet_(play)" title="Mahomet (play)">Mahomet</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=M%C3%A9rope&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Mérope (page does not exist)">Mérope</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Nanine" title="Nanine">Nanine</a></i></li>
<li><i>The Orphan of China</i> (1755)<sup id="cite_ref-23" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-23" title=""><span>[</span>24<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
</ul>
