<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> This is a translation of a famous Chinese play <a href="/wiki/Orphan_of_Zhao" title="Orphan of Zhao">Orphan of Zhao</a> about the revenge of the orphan of the clan of Zhao on his enemies who killed almost every member of his clan. This play was based on an actual historical event in the Spring-Autumn period of Chinese history. Voltaire's version was translated by <a href="/wiki/Arthur_Murphy" title="Arthur Murphy">Arthur Murphy</a> as <i>The Orphan of China</i> in 1759.</li>
</ol>
